    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-05-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-05-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="468" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d468">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Uhl</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Baker</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-05-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 22,
                                1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your dispatch and Watson’s report prove culpable responsibility for
                            Argüello’s escape. Ask instant effective rebuke and redress. Instruction
                            mailed 12th to demand Torres’ removal. Lacayo’s culpability appears even
                            greater because more directly responsible.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
